63rd Drive, at Carlton Avenue, looking northeast and showing the Suydâm farmhouse. It was owned by Suydam from 1860 to 1873. The Stoothoffs owned it from 1891 to 1896. The farmhouse is located on the line of Dieterle Crescent, just south of Alderton Street.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
April, 1923
